  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is designed to evaluate effects of NSAIDs on immune activity inside and close to
      tumor tissue in patients with colorectal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study and control patients are randomized to receive preoperative treatment with indomethacin
      or celecoxib compared to sham treatment.Tumor biopsies are taken at operation and used for
      analyses of tumor immunity and gene expression.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
